AI-specific incidents (harmful output, discrimination, malfunction affecting a user's rights) are handled under our [Incident Response Plan](./incident-response-plan.md). {{#if system.euMarket}}For this system, placed on the EU market, serious incidents are additionally reported to the relevant market surveillance authority under EU AI Act Article 73 without undue delay.{{/if}}

